Conditional execution: Three examples
========================================================

**Example 1**

```{r}
a <- 1
b <- 2

if(a==1) c <- b
print(c)
```


Conditional execution: Three examples
========================================================

**Example 2**

```{r}
a <- 1
b <- 2

if(a==2) {
  c <- b
  } else {
    c <- a+b
}

print(c)
```

Conditional execution: Three examples
========================================================

**Example 3**

```{r}
a <- 1
b <- 2

ifelse(a==2, c <- b, c <- a+b)
```



